Emery: &ldquo;Right now, I can say that our motivation is at the highest level to succeed in both the Premier League &amp; the Europa League. My message to the fans is that they believe in us &amp; above all that they show their support towards Los Gunners.&rdquo; #afc<br />
<br />
Emery: &ldquo;When you lose everything looks bad &amp; you want to change everything &amp; when you win, it&rsquo;s the opposite. It&rsquo;s a case of being patient at some moments &amp; finding balance. You have to understand things that need to improve in victory &amp; also things that are good even in defeat.&rdquo;
